snippet.title: Sparky: Hills of Death - Gameplay Trailer #1
snippet.description:
First trailer of Sparky Hills of Death, my game created by @Gabizini  and developed by @maninstudios1  showcasing current gameplay, lore, cutscenes, and more. I hope you enjoy this trailer, our team has put a lot of dedication into this game, so enjoy!
